<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yswʿ ạ̉nt hnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yswʿ ạ̉nt hnạ
 (yạ mlạdẖ ạ̉rwạḥnạ .. yạ sẖfạʾ nfwsnạ)2
 1- (yạ mqym ạlsạqṭyn .. ạlgẖrqy̱ fy ṭyn ạlạ̉tẖạm
 yạ rjạʾ ạlbạỷsyn .. ạlmnṭwyyn fy ạlḥṭạm)2
 (yạ mynạʾ ạltạỷhyn .. ạlywm fy ʿṣf ạlryḥ
 yạ mʿyn ạllạjỷyyn .. fwḥdk ạlbạb ạlmtạḥ)2
 2- (yạ mjyb ạlṣạrkẖyyn .. ạ̹lyk yạ bạb ạlnjạẗ
 yạ kẖlạṣ ạlhạlkyn .. yạ mn ṣlbt ʿn ạlkẖṭạẗ)2
 (yạ mqwm ạlạ̹nḥnạʾ .. yạ mn yḥl ạlmạ̉swryn
 yạ yswʿ ạ̉nt ʿzạʾ .. kl ṣgẖyr ạlqlb ḥzyn)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1541</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
</song>